channel.title: Your Internet Friend, Jimmy Marks
channel.description: My name is Jimmy Marks and I am your Internet friend. Does that mean we're only friends on the Internet? Depends...we ever meet in real life? I'll be your real life friend, too, but mostly I'm there to help you do fun and nice things on the Internet.
